==Useful Info==
'''Giant cockroaches''' are common pests found all throughout the early [[Dungeon]]. They are faster than the average character, but only pose a threat to low level characters on the brink of death.

==Tips & Tricks==
*Their AC can pose a problem for characters with weak starting attacks, particularly those with low-power L1 spells. Don't be afraid to beat them with an unskilled melee weapon if your spells are repeatedly doing no damage.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.25]], giant cockroaches could [[cling]] onto walls in order to travel through adjacent water.
*Prior to [[0.15]], chunks of giant cockroach meat were contaminated.
